Many of us have heard discussions or read in books

00:28:13.010 --> 00:28:17.370
about the evolution of matter, the evolution of the substance.

00:28:18.170 --> 00:28:21.170
What are Your views on evolving matter

00:28:21.370 --> 00:28:24.210
and how does this relate to our own physical matter

00:28:24.450 --> 00:28:26.290
in our bodies or cells?

00:28:26.490 --> 00:28:29.330
So the matter did go into evolution, you know that,

