00:31:47.690 --> 00:31:49.810
you cannot do sex with your brain, you see.

00:31:50.050 --> 00:31:51.730
So it’s all a nonsensical thing.

00:31:51.930 --> 00:31:54.690
All these things have added to your problems

00:31:54.890 --> 00:31:57.370
of impotency and all sorts of things in this country.

