00:32:10.570 --> 00:32:12.810
To be natural is to keep it spontaneous,

00:32:13.010 --> 00:32:14.570
to live very spontaneously.

00:32:14.770 --> 00:32:17.790
Of course, as an Indian lady, it is too much to speak on details

00:32:17.990 --> 00:32:20.050
but I would say that…

00:32:23.280 --> 00:32:27.240
