So the sex which is a normal thing to do

00:34:36.610 --> 00:34:39.810
has to be sanctified by collective people,

00:34:40.010 --> 00:34:41.660
should be done in a proper way

00:34:41.860 --> 00:34:43.400
so that you get good children.

00:34:43.610 --> 00:34:46.610
The marriage should be sanctified collectively

00:34:46.810 --> 00:34:49.050
and should be done in a proper way

00:34:49.250 --> 00:34:50.700
and should be looked after.

